### Agirlik mode with custom cap and multiplier
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: image/png

{
  "w": 384,
  "h": 256,
  "tiles": "1x1*100,2x1*150,3x3*40",
  "ka": 1.5,
  "cap": 600,
  "mode": "agirlik",
  "rot": 0
}

